{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-153","title":"无聊寂寞","sectionId":"chapter-07","sectionTitle":"喜怒哀乐听你说","pageStart":771,"pageEnd":775,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":18,"duplicateEntryCount":19,"pages":[{"number":771,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"153 无聊寂寞"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"dullness [ˈdʌlnəs]","headword":"dullness"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.乏味"},{"type":"entry","text":"loneliness [ˈləʊnlinəs]","headword":"loneliness"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.孤独"},{"type":"note","text":"◎emotional loneliness情感孤独"},{"type":"entry","text":"lonely [ˈləʊnli]","headword":"lonely"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.孤独的（强调孤独感）"},{"type":"note","text":"◎lonely days孤独的日子"},{"type":"entry","text":"alone [əˈləʊn]","headword":"alone"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.单独的，独自的（指独自一人的状态）"}]},{"number":772,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"◎leave sb. alone不烦扰某人"},{"type":"entry","text":"lonesome [ˈləʊnsəm]","headword":"lonesome"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.寂寞的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎by one's lonesome独自；孤立地"},{"type":"entry","text":"isolated [ˈaɪsəleɪtɪd]","headword":"isolated"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.与世隔绝的；孤立的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎isolated area隔离区"}]},{"number":773,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"bored [bɔːd]","headword":"bored"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.无聊的，无趣的；厌倦的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎get bored变得厌倦"},{"type":"entry","text":"tiresome [ˈtaɪəsəm]","headword":"tiresome"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.无聊的，令人讨厌的（使人厌倦，使人疲惫）"},{"type":"entry","text":"uninteresting [ʌnˈɪntrəstɪŋ]","headword":"uninteresting"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.无趣的"},{"type":"entry","text":"unimaginative [ˌʌnɪˈmædʒɪnətɪv]","headword":"unimaginative"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.无趣的"}]},{"number":774,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"toneless [ˈtəʊnləs]","headword":"toneless"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.沉闷的；单调的"},{"type":"entry","text":"lengthy [ˈleŋθi]","headword":"lengthy"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.漫长的，冗长的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎lengthy wait漫长的等待"},{"type":"entry","text":"being all alone 独自一人","headword":"being all alone"},{"type":"entry","text":"alone time 独处时间","headword":"alone time"},{"type":"entry","text":"all alone 独自","headword":"all alone"},{"type":"entry","text":"lone wolf 喜欢孤独的人","headword":"lone wolf"},{"type":"entry","text":"on one's own 独自地","headword":"on one's own"},{"type":"entry","text":"by oneself 独自地","headword":"by oneself"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"}]},{"number":775,"blocks":[{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：If you feel lonely, call me and we can talk. （如果你觉得寂寞，"},{"type":"text","text":"打电话给我，我们可以聊聊。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：OK, thanks. （好的，多谢。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Do you think you're living in a sort of isolated world? （你是否认"},{"type":"text","text":"为你生活在一个孤立的世界里？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Yes, I feel so sometimes. （是的，我有时有这种感觉。）"}]}]}